::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor walks over to the fallen Airbomber, looking at Infectra and aiming 
his gun at the two of them. His finger begins to move, starting to pull the 
trigger when Black Arachnia's transmission comes through.

He snaps into a salute, instantly running off toward Megs' cave.
